## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React 18, TypeScript 5, Vite 5
- **Backend**: Rust, Tauri 2.x
- **Build**: pnpm, Cargo
- **Testing**: Vitest (frontend), Rust tests (backend)

## Prerequisites

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) 18+
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) 9+
- [Rust](https://rustup.rs/) 1.75+
- Platform-specific dependencies:
- **macOS**: Xcode Command Line Tools
- **Windows**: Microsoft Visual C++ Build Tools, WebView2
- **Linux**: See [Tauri prerequisites](https://tauri.app/start/prerequisites/#linux)

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
make install

# Run in development mode
make dev

# Build for production
make build-release
```

## Development

### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `make dev` | Start development server with hot reload |
| `make build` | Build debug version |
| `make build-release` | Build production release |
| `make test` | Run frontend tests |
| `make lint` | Lint all code |
| `make format` | Format all code |
| `make typecheck` | Check TypeScript types |
| `make clean` | Clean build artifacts |

